name: Supertech Sportistaan Villas

Come Explore Supertech Sportistaan A World Class Sports Centric Residential Development Supertech Sportistaan is a new project by the Reputed Player- Supertech. The Exquisite Residential Project is located in Noida Extension, closer to Proposed Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) Cricket Stadium. 

The Grand Project Presents Ultra-Modern Villas -4 BHK+4T- with 2400 SQ. FT. Area to cater to the needs of the Elite Class. Astonishing Villas are perfectly designed by the experts to grab the attention of the potential buyers. It is a perfect place for people who love Sports as it is going to be a Mecca of Sports.
